name: Self Portrait with Subcutaneous Polychronic Vision Enhancer [Cryptoborg #12]
description:
You're here for Zeta's latest upgrade – An 'S/P Vision Enhancer' grafted onto her left temple. The specifications describe it as 'number-pattern' optimised and 'axsys-oecumenic' consistent.

The SPVE is a photo-impulse converter for the recently installed The Axon-Maker™ 'Ocu-Eye' It facilitates scene reconstruction, object and event detection, video tracking and motion sensing.
